Notification : Successor

The UN{United Nation}Compensation Commission (UNCC) on recommendations of
International Monitoring Group (IMG) have agreed to compensate Scam Victims
and failed international Business/government contract which occured due to
Government problems with the sum of One Million Two Hundred Thousand
Dollars (USD$1.200, 000.00). This development is based on a meeting we had
for the past two weeks which ended Two days ago with the World Bank
President Dr. Robert B. Rollick and Hon. Mrs. Christine Laggard (IMF)
Director General.

A payment have been arranged through ATM VISA CARD or direct transfer
into your bank account which is the latest instruction from World Bank
Group.

It was made to let you know that this information is made only for the
concerned person,please do not give a Feedback/Reply if you are not
involved in any of the aforementioned. BEWARE,DON'T CLAIM.

Contact email address : elizabethcastro6453@gmail.com,with your
details as shown below for further instruction.
